FEATURES
========
[x] Solid mode
[~] Gradient mode
  [ ] Pulse brightness option
  [ ] Rotate option (gradient moves along strip, last colour blends back to first)
  [ ] Allow more than 2 colours
[~] Sequence mode
  [x] List of colours
  [x] Blend to next, loop
  [ ] Sequence of gradients as well as solid colour
  [ ] Show each colour for X seconds
  [ ] Select colours from front end and pass through to back end

